  "keyFeatures": [
    "ANTLR4-generated lexer, parser, and visitor from a single grammar file",
    "Cantor pairing function for encoding multiple inputs as a single natural number",
    "Core combinators: comp, pair, compair, mu (minimization), primrec (primitive recursion)",
